data.description: Amazing house near downtown Chandler! 3 bed / 2 updated bathrooms. Open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, a wood burning fireplace, and custom blinds. The kitchen was newly remodeled 3 years ago with all new appliances, dual pane windows, and fresh paint. The home is situated on a corner lot with a newly re-plastered pool and pool pump. Don't forget both a 2 car garage and a carport. Look no further, this house has it all!
